  "instructions": [
    "proof yeast in warm water for 5 minutes",
    "mix dough ingredients and knead for 10 minutes",
    "rest dough for 1 hour",
    "divide dough into 6 equal pieces",
    "roll out each piece into a thin circle",
    "brush with melted butter and sprinkle with sugar",
    "place a small spoonful of elderflower syrup and rice vinegar in the centre",
    "fold dough into a bao shape and press edges together to seal",
    "heat a non-stick pan over medium heat and cook bao for 2 minutes on each side",
    "serve warm and garnish with sesame seeds"
